	This is the config file of Asura, where you can set everything what's normally needed.
	To change the launcher icon, change the file "ic_launcher.png" in the drawable folders.
	Do not forget to change the application id in 'app/build.gradle'!
	
	Checklist:
	- 1. Change application id
	- 2. Change application icon
	- 3. Fill out this file (config.xml)
	
	Index:
	- 1. General (Name, JSON URL, ...)
	- 2. Preferences (About, Contact)
	- 3. Menu Items
	- 4. Data
-->
